nodes.text: Moshi Bar was a tavern located in the underworld of the planet Coruscant. It was owned and operated by Tiggs Leo, a Volpai male bartender, during the Clone Wars. While searching for information on the whereabouts of Boba Fett and Aurra Sing, Jedi Master Plo Koon and Padawan Ahsoka Tano visited the tavern.

Moshi Bar first appeared in "Lethal Trackdown," the twenty-second episode of the canon animated series Star Wars: The Clone Wars' second season. Although it went unnamed in its sole appearance, the tavern was identified as Moshi Bar in concept art available on the Blu-ray version of Star Wars: The Clone Wars The Complete Season Two.
